1. Search for App services and create give name, select python3.14, select region --> central india enter next till validation and create it.

2. Go to created resources then go to Deployment Center and choose github, choose account, choose repo --> Azure-appservices --> save it.

3. Go to overview and click on default domain you will see your application.

4. If you make any changes in code on github it will auto sync and do modification in application.



